{"id":"0TFVNeFA6dVofKsw","meta":{"instanceId":"bc8ca75c203589705ae2e446cad7181d6f2a7cc1766f958ef9f34810e53b8cb2","templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"name":"FAQ Audio Generator — Form + OpenAI TTS + Google Drive + Sheets + Gmail","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"768f4d85-15e7-4a04-8dac-706b87351d7d","name":"Overview","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-624,-480],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":492,"height":1220,"content":"## FAQ Audio Generator — Form + OpenAI TTS + Google Drive + Sheets + Gmail\n\nFor support, docs, and course teams who want a written FAQ library turned into shareable audio without an enterprise stack. Fill a form with up to 5 FAQ entries (question and answer, plus a category). Each FAQ is converted into a professional MP3 using OpenAI text-to-speech, saved to Google Drive, logged in Google Sheets with its audio link, and emailed back to you as a complete summary with all the links.\n\n## How it works\n- **1. Form — FAQ Entry Input** collects your email, a category, and up to 5 question-and-answer pairs\n- **2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items** turns the filled pairs into one item per FAQ and builds a spoken script and filename for each\n- **3. HTTP — OpenAI TTS Generate MP3** converts each FAQ script into an MP3 voice file\n- **4. Google Drive — Save MP3 File** uploads each MP3 to your Drive folder\n- **5. Code — Store Drive URL and FAQ Data** builds the listen and download links for each file\n- **6. Sheets — Log FAQ and Audio URL** appends each FAQ with its links to the log\n- **7. Aggregate — Collect All Processed FAQs** gathers every processed FAQ into one item\n- **8. Code — Build Summary Email** builds the HTML summary with all audio links\n- **9. Gmail — Send Audio Summary** emails you the complete summary\n\n## Set up steps\n1. **OpenAI** — in **3. HTTP — OpenAI TTS Generate MP3**, connect your OpenAI API credential. TTS bills per character — a typical FAQ answer costs a fraction of a cent\n2. **Google Drive** — create a folder for the audio, copy its folder ID from the URL after /folders/, replace `YOUR_AUDIO_FOLDER_ID` in node 4, and connect Google Drive OAuth2\n3. **Google Sheets** — create a sheet with a tab named FAQs and these columns: Date, Category, Question, Answer Preview, Audio URL, Download URL, Drive File ID, Filename. Replace `YOUR_FAQ_LOG_SHEET_ID` in node 6 and connect Google Sheets OAuth2\n4. **Gmail** — connect Gmail OAuth2 in node 9. The recipient comes from the form\n5. Activate the workflow, open the Form URL, enter your FAQs, and submit. The summary email arrives with every audio link"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"ccd99444-7357-4921-b29c-897f8dacb63d","name":"Section — Form Input and FAQ Parsing","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-32,-128],"parameters":{"color":5,"width":404,"height":452,"content":"## Form Input and FAQ Parsing\nForm collects up to 5 FAQ pairs (question, answer, and a shared category). Code parses the filled pairs into individual items — one per FAQ — each with its own spoken script and filename."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"697d190f-bc31-4025-8276-7978049cbb36","name":"Section — Text-to-Speech and Drive Save","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[416,-256],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":708,"height":820,"content":"## Text-to-Speech and Drive Save\nEach FAQ item is processed in turn. OpenAI text-to-speech generates the MP3 voice file, Google Drive saves it, and Code builds the listen and download links."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8019cd81-714d-45a2-98c0-e6de19892597","name":"Section — Log and Email Summary","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1136,-112],"parameters":{"color":4,"width":1092,"height":468,"content":"## Log and Email Summary\nSheets logs every FAQ with its audio links. Aggregate collects all processed FAQs, Code builds the summary, and Gmail sends the full email with clickable audio links."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"216a643d-98ec-41d3-92e6-b6c81adcf452","name":"1. Form — FAQ Entry Input","type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","position":[0,64],"webhookId":"817c2a8b-74ac-48da-8946-cb866e8bd785","parameters":{"options":{"path":"faq-audio-generator","buttonLabel":"Generate Audio Files","appendAttribution":false},"formTitle":"FAQ Audio Generator","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Your Email Address","placeholder":"your@email.com — summary will be sent here","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"FAQ Category","placeholder":"e.g. Getting Started, Billing, Technical Support, Account","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Question 1","placeholder":"e.g. How do I reset my password?","requiredField":true},{"fieldType":"textarea","fieldLabel":"Answer 1","placeholder":"Full answer text — this will be read aloud by TTS","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Question 2","placeholder":"e.g. How do I upgrade my plan?"},{"fieldType":"textarea","fieldLabel":"Answer 2","placeholder":"Full answer text"},{"fieldLabel":"Question 3","placeholder":"Optional — third FAQ question"},{"fieldType":"textarea","fieldLabel":"Answer 3","placeholder":"Full answer text"},{"fieldLabel":"Question 4","placeholder":"Optional — fourth FAQ question"},{"fieldType":"textarea","fieldLabel":"Answer 4","placeholder":"Full answer text"},{"fieldLabel":"Question 5","placeholder":"Optional — fifth FAQ question"},{"fieldType":"textarea","fieldLabel":"Answer 5","placeholder":"Full answer text"}]},"formDescription":"Enter your FAQ entries below. Each FAQ will be converted into a professional MP3 audio file, saved to Google Drive, and you will receive a summary email with all audio links."},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"03a731d8-0f55-4866-bd1e-61b16ce3c185","name":"2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[240,64],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const row      = $json;\nconst email    = (row['Your Email Address'] || '').trim();\nconst category = (row['FAQ Category']       || 'General').trim();\nconst today    = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];\n\nif (!email)    throw new Error('Email address is required.');\nif (!category) throw new Error('FAQ Category is required.');\n\nconst faqs = [];\nfor (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {\n  const q = (row['Question ' + i] || '').trim();\n  const a = (row['Answer '   + i] || '').trim();\n  if (!q || !a) continue;\n  if (a.length < 10) continue;\n\n  const ttsScript = [\n    category + '.',\n    q,\n    '...',\n    a\n  ].join(' ');\n\n  const safeName = q\n    .toLowerCase()\n    .replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g, '-')\n    .replace(/-+/g, '-')\n    .replace(/^-|-$/g, '')\n    .substring(0, 50);\n\n  faqs.push({\n    faqIndex:      i,\n    category,\n    question:      q,\n    answer:        a,\n    answerPreview: a.substring(0, 100) + (a.length > 100 ? '...' : ''),\n    ttsScript,\n    filename:      'faq-' + category.toLowerCase().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g, '-') + '-' + i + '-' + safeName + '.mp3',\n    email,\n    date:          today\n  });\n}\n\nif (faqs.length === 0) {\n  throw new Error('No valid FAQ pairs found. Please fill at least Question 1 and Answer 1.');\n}\n\nreturn faqs.map(f => ({ json: f }));"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"85586ba1-376a-4e39-b88a-66befe533927","name":"3. HTTP — OpenAI TTS Generate MP3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[480,64],"parameters":{"url":"https://api.openai.com/v1/audio/speech","method":"POST","options":{"timeout":60000,"response":{"response":{"responseFormat":"file"}}},"jsonBody":"={\n  \"model\": \"tts-1\",\n  \"input\": {{ JSON.stringify($json.ttsScript) }},\n  \"voice\": \"alloy\",\n  \"response_format\": \"mp3\"\n}","sendBody":true,"sendHeaders":true,"specifyBody":"json","authentication":"predefinedCredentialType","headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}]},"nodeCredentialType":"openAiApi"},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"f0db988a-08b9-4af4-956e-2347c037bb55","name":"4. Google Drive — Save MP3 File","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive","position":[720,64],"parameters":{"name":"={{ $('2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items').item.json.filename }}","driveId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"My Drive","cachedResultName":"My Drive"},"options":{},"folderId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_AUDIO_FOLDER_ID"}},"typeVersion":3},{"id":"7e1aeefd-797e-48de-9763-963caf77b4e7","name":"5. Code — Store Drive URL and FAQ Data","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[960,64],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const driveItem = $json;\nconst faqData   = $('2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items').item.json;\n\nconst fileId = driveItem.id || '';\nif (!fileId) throw new Error('Drive did not return a file ID for: ' + faqData.filename);\n\nconst audioUrl    = 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/' + fileId + '/view?usp=sharing';\nconst downloadUrl = 'https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=' + fileId;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...faqData,\n    driveFileId:  fileId,\n    audioUrl,\n    downloadUrl,\n    driveWebViewLink: driveItem.webViewLink || audioUrl\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"688a7792-9026-4178-90de-6b83c69899f7","name":"6. Sheets — Log FAQ and Audio URL","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[1200,64],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Date":"={{ $json.date }}","Category":"={{ $json.category }}","Filename":"={{ $json.filename }}","Question":"={{ $json.question }}","Audio URL":"={{ $json.audioUrl }}","Download URL":"={{ $json.downloadUrl }}","Drive File ID":"={{ $json.driveFileId }}","Answer Preview":"={{ $json.answerPreview }}"},"schema":[{"id":"Date","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Date","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Category","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Category","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Question","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Question","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Answer Preview","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Answer Preview","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Audio URL","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Audio URL","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Download URL","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Download URL","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Drive File ID","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Drive File ID","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Filename","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Filename","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true}],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":[],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":true},"options":{},"operation":"append","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"FAQs"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_FAQ_LOG_SHEET_ID"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"119afac7-34d9-4d55-9ff2-f3444944c1c8","name":"7. Aggregate — Collect All Processed FAQs","type":"n8n-nodes-base.aggregate","position":[1440,64],"parameters":{"options":{},"aggregate":"aggregateAllItemData","destinationFieldName":"allFaqs"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"8918b5bd-b510-4d3e-94c1-87cfb7281d99","name":"8. Code — Build Summary Email","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[1680,64],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const allFaqs = $input.first().json.allFaqs || [];\nconst first    = allFaqs[0] || {};\nconst email    = first.email    || 'YOUR_EMAIL_ADDRESS';\nconst category = first.category || 'FAQ Audio Library';\nconst today    = first.date     || new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];\n\nconst faqRows = allFaqs.map(f =>\n  '<tr>' +\n  '<td style=\"padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;color:#1a1a2e;\">' +\n    '<strong>' + f.question + '</strong>' +\n    '<br><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;\">' + f.answerPreview + '</span>' +\n  '</td>' +\n  '<td style=\"padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;\">' +\n    '<a href=\"' + f.audioUrl + '\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#4a90e2;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;\">Listen</a>' +\n    '&nbsp;&nbsp;' +\n    '<a href=\"' + f.downloadUrl + '\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#eee;color:#333;text-decoration:none;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;\">MP3</a>' +\n  '</td>' +\n  '</tr>'\n).join('');\n\nconst htmlBody = '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"></head>' +\n'<body style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;background:#f5f5f5;\">' +\n\n'<div style=\"background:#1a1a2e;padding:24px 28px;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;\">' +\n'<h1 style=\"color:#fff;font-size:20px;margin:0;\">FAQ Audio Library</h1>' +\n'<p style=\"color:#90caf9;font-size:13px;margin:6px 0 0;\">Category: ' + category + ' &nbsp;|&nbsp; ' + allFaqs.length + ' audio files generated &nbsp;|&nbsp; ' + today + '</p>' +\n'</div>' +\n\n'<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;padding:16px 24px;\">' +\n'<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#2e7d32;\">All ' + allFaqs.length + ' FAQ audio files have been generated and saved to Google Drive. Click the links below to listen or download each MP3.</p>' +\n'</div>' +\n\n'<div style=\"background:#fff;padding:16px 24px;\">' +\n'<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\">' +\n'<thead><tr style=\"background:#f0f4ff;\">' +\n'<th style=\"padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-size:12px;color:#444;border-bottom:2px solid #ddd;\">Question and Answer Preview</th>' +\n'<th style=\"padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#444;border-bottom:2px solid #ddd;\">Audio</th>' +\n'</tr></thead>' +\n'<tbody>' + faqRows + '</tbody>' +\n'</table>' +\n'</div>' +\n\n'<div style=\"background:#f0f4ff;padding:14px 24px;\">' +\n'<p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#333;\"><strong>All files saved to:</strong> Google Drive, FAQ Audio Library, ' + category + '</p>' +\n'<p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">To make these files publicly accessible, share your FAQ Audio Library folder as anyone-with-link can view.</p>' +\n'</div>' +\n\n'<div style=\"background:#1a1a2e;padding:12px 24px;text-align:center;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;\">' +\n'<p style=\"color:#90caf9;font-size:11px;margin:0;\">FAQ Audio Generator — n8n + OpenAI TTS + Google Drive</p>' +\n'</div>' +\n\n'</body></html>';\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    email,\n    category,\n    faqCount: allFaqs.length,\n    htmlBody,\n    emailSubject: 'FAQ Audio Ready — ' + allFaqs.length + ' files in ' + category + ' | ' + today\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"2bc233ea-d1ff-4bb3-a6fa-eb88424ef1cd","name":"9. Gmail — Send Audio Summary","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[1920,64],"webhookId":"18e22adf-b474-4e14-881c-709cf4a09177","parameters":{"sendTo":"={{ $json.email }}","message":"={{ $json.htmlBody }}","options":{"senderName":"FAQ Audio Generator"},"subject":"={{ $json.emailSubject }}"},"typeVersion":2.1}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"2cdbcb51-94bd-410a-b236-9caefc5d6a30","nodeGroups":[],"connections":{"1. Form — FAQ Entry Input":{"main":[[{"node":"2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"8. Code — Build Summary Email":{"main":[[{"node":"9. Gmail — Send Audio Summary","type":"main","index":0}]]},"4. Google Drive — Save MP3 File":{"main":[[{"node":"5. Code — Store Drive URL and FAQ Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"3. HTTP — OpenAI TTS Generate MP3":{"main":[[{"node":"4. Google Drive — Save MP3 File","type":"main","index":0}]]},"6. Sheets — Log FAQ and Audio URL":{"main":[[{"node":"7. Aggregate — Collect All Processed FAQs","type":"main","index":0}]]},"2. Code — Parse FAQ Pairs into Items":{"main":[[{"node":"3. HTTP — OpenAI TTS Generate MP3","type":"main","index":0}]]},"5. Code — Store Drive URL and FAQ Data":{"main":[[{"node":"6. Sheets — Log FAQ and Audio URL","type":"main","index":0}]]},"7. Aggregate — Collect All Processed FAQs":{"main":[[{"node":"8. Code — Build Summary Email","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}